  "text": "A central component of a Bayesian anthropology is an appreciation of plural priors going into a world of probabilities. What do I mean by this? Let me put it in the way I did when I taught statistics to Irvine anthropology graduate students. I also did something very like this over a decade ago when I was first writing about financial derivatives [CITATION_1] .",
